00:25:46.520 --> 00:25:50.409
1997-1231_Shakti Puja talk Kalwe, India

00:25:50.610 --> 00:25:56.537
I was telling them about the Shakti, is the woman.

00:25:56.737 --> 00:26:01.263
Man cannot do without the woman, she’s the power behind him.

00:26:01.463 --> 00:26:04.657
But how you treat your Shakti is very important.

00:26:04.857 --> 00:26:08.397
How you look after your wife is very important.

00:26:08.597 --> 00:26:11.440
I was telling them in the West marriages are broken,

00:26:11.640 --> 00:26:16.290
families are broken, the children are on the road

00:26:16.490 --> 00:26:20.630
and there is no discipline at all,

00:26:20.831 --> 00:26:24.322
no discipline of any kind.

00:26:24.523 --> 00:26:27.583
You can’t say what sort of children they’ll be tomorrow.

00:26:27.783 --> 00:26:30.643
They could be devils. They could be anything,

00:26:30.843 --> 00:26:35.810
because parents have no interest in their children

00:26:36.010 --> 00:26:39.497
and parents have no interest in themselves.

00:26:39.697 --> 00:26:43.350
So first of all, the family has to be all right.

00:26:43.550 --> 00:26:45.570
You must know that you have married.

00:26:45.771 --> 00:26:49.317
So many people got married now in Sahaja Yoga.

00:26:49.517 --> 00:26:52.677
So I have to tell them: at the very outset,

00:26:52.877 --> 00:26:57.710
you must decide that you’ll see the good points of your partner.

00:26:57.910 --> 00:27:00.160
And you must promise and take a challenge

00:27:00.360 --> 00:27:05.277
that "we are going to make a very happy married life".

00:27:05.477 --> 00:27:10.090
Very easy to find faults with others, because your eyes are outward.

00:27:10.290 --> 00:27:13.800
If you could somehow turn them inside, you’ll be surprised

00:27:14.000 --> 00:27:19.603
that you have many more defects then they have.

00:27:21.250 --> 00:27:25.890
And it’s the responsibility of the women to look after the society.

00:27:26.090 --> 00:27:31.063
If something has gone wrong with your society it is because of the women,

00:27:31.263 --> 00:27:39.090
who don’t understand what is their job, what is their duty.

00:27:39.290 --> 00:27:45.530
And their attention has gone so low

00:27:45.730 --> 00:27:49.190
that they try to compare themselves with the cheap women,

00:27:49.390 --> 00:27:51.670
with the cheap actresses

00:27:51.870 --> 00:27:57.530
and also women without any ideals in their life.

00:27:57.730 --> 00:28:00.237
You being Sahaja yogis, you have to understand

00:28:00.437 --> 00:28:06.850
that you’re not like these horrible women, you are a special type.

00:28:07.050 --> 00:28:10.483
And you must not take to all the stupid thing

00:28:10.683 --> 00:28:14.797
that these women are doing for money. It amounts to prostitution,

00:28:14.998 --> 00:28:18.737
I think, the way things people are doing for money.

00:28:18.937 --> 00:28:22.423
So be satisfied.

00:28:22.623 --> 00:28:25.910
And if you are satisfied,

00:28:26.111 --> 00:28:30.217
you’ll really enjoy yourself, you’ll enjoy your family life.

00:28:30.417 --> 00:28:34.850
The woman who is not satisfied always finds faults with others,

00:28:35.050 --> 00:28:38.983
always is demanding something, can never make a good wife

00:28:39.183 --> 00:28:43.070
and can never make a good society.

00:28:43.270 --> 00:28:52.037
And this society which she will make will destroy the next society.

00:28:53.523 --> 00:28:56.130
Of course the men must respect women

00:28:56.330 --> 00:28:59.143
and respect the great qualities in them.

00:28:59.343 --> 00:29:03.782
Their satisfaction, their patience, their understanding,

00:29:03.983 --> 00:29:06.077
everything must be respected.

00:29:06.277 --> 00:29:09.950
And they should not make fun of their wives all the time.

00:29:10.150 --> 00:29:14.137
I have seen, if that is done then women stoop down to the same level.

00:29:14.337 --> 00:29:18.177
That’s no friendship. In friendship, you must have respect.

00:29:18.403 --> 00:29:20.763
It’s all right, you can do this with your friends,

00:29:20.963 --> 00:29:25.363
but not with your wife. And this is what I can’t understand,

00:29:25.563 --> 00:29:33.169
that how men use their intelligence in such a stupid manner.

00:29:33.370 --> 00:29:36.337
Because she is the mother of your children.

00:29:36.537 --> 00:29:39.917
If you make fun of her, children will also make fun of her.

00:29:40.117 --> 00:29:42.150
Of course she has to respect you,

00:29:42.351 --> 00:29:45.030
because she receives her authority from you,

00:29:45.230 --> 00:29:48.777
but also you must maintain her authority.

00:29:48.977 --> 00:29:54.197
You must keep her in proper shape.

00:29:54.397 --> 00:29:59.190
For small things, husbands give up their wives and misbehave.

00:29:59.390 --> 00:30:04.677
It’s more shocking that some of the senior people in Sahaja Yoga

00:30:04.877 --> 00:30:08.743
have done all kinds of nonsense about their married life.

00:30:08.943 --> 00:30:13.277
I am amazed at them. How could they do it?

00:30:13.477 --> 00:30:17.840
And this really shocks Me. I was told that this year,

00:30:18.040 --> 00:30:22.710
on coming here, will be Sahaja yogis who will go astray,

00:30:22.910 --> 00:30:28.617
they’ll do dirty things, bad things and, I should say,

00:30:28.817 --> 00:30:36.416
things which are not pure and they will destroy Sahaja Yoga.

00:30:36.617 --> 00:30:39.763
If they are predicted like that, you can imagine at this age of Mine,

00:30:39.963 --> 00:30:42.057
I’ll have to fight it.

00:30:42.257 --> 00:30:46.077
But you all can fight it by understanding that it’s not your life,

00:30:46.277 --> 00:30:51.243
this is not a Sahaja life and you have to live in a Sahaja manner,

00:30:51.443 --> 00:30:54.057
must bring a good name to Sahaja Yoga.

00:30:54.257 --> 00:30:57.397
Not artificially but really, people should say that

00:30:57.597 --> 00:31:03.390
if they have met any saints, they are in Sahaja Yoga.

00:31:04.143 --> 00:31:10.830
The other day also, I said that miserliness
is not the quality of a Sahaja Yogi.

00:31:11.030 --> 00:31:15.643
Because he knows he’ll get whatever he wants.

00:31:15.843 --> 00:31:19.543
Should go on distributing as much as you can.

00:31:19.743 --> 00:31:24.943
All this is going to work out in the favor.

00:31:25.143 --> 00:31:28.197
More than men, women are miserly.

00:31:28.397 --> 00:31:31.657
They’ll look after their children but not others’ children,

00:31:31.857 --> 00:31:34.563
not other people.

00:31:34.763 --> 00:31:38.830
So if the women become more socialistic, it would be a better idea.

00:31:39.030 --> 00:31:47.403
And it will help them a lot to do justice to their own shakti,

00:31:47.603 --> 00:31:52.877
because she wants, your shakti within wants you to be generous,

00:31:53.077 --> 00:31:55.157
to be kind, to be loving.

00:31:55.357 --> 00:32:01.503
If you are not loving then it’s not going to work out.
